name: Ningbo Hosting Elevator Company
description: Ningbo Hosting Elevator Co., Ltd. was set up in 1993. We are Elevator Manufacturers, Passenger Elevator Manufacturers, Escalator Manufacturer. in Europe, the Americas, the Middle East, Southeast Asia, Africa.Hosting elevator is a national key new technology-based firm and a professional elevator and escalator manufacturer. We are Escalator Manufacturer, Passenger Lift Manufacturer, Bed Elevators Manufacturer, Cargo Elevator Manufacturer.

name: Ningbo Hosting Elevator Company Video
description: HOSTING Elevator, a subsidiary of XINDA Group, was established in 1993. HOSTING Elevator is a national key new technology enterprise. It is a professional elevator and escalator manufacturer integrating development, manufacturing, installation and maintenance. Our products are widely used in government-funded projects, real estate projects, hotels and urban rail transit projects. More than 30% of our products are exported to South America, Europe, Asia, Middle East, Africa and other countries; our export volume ranks in China's top 10, HOSTING Elevators rank among the best in China's own brands.
